Description: Developed a personal website to display professional and academic experiences.
Refactored a financial account-opening system to support domain-driven design, upgrading it to use newer technologies where needed.
Designed and developed a web app to spawn shell scripts that automate Syncsort DMX-h and Informatica PowerCenter workflows.
Designed and developed shell scripts to update Informatica PowerCenter workflows' data sources and targets.
Designed and developed an interactive bubble chart displaying employee utilization via collision-detecting, animated bubbles.
Developed a data-driven web app for users to monitor and manage project metadata.
Developed the user interface for a web app through which judges score mini-game players and users view results in a leaderboard format.
Scoped, designed, and developed a virtual "message in a bottle" Android app, letting users place and encounter messages while traveling.
Edited the Guild Wars 2 wiki and created character templates for wiki-editors to display on their user pages.
